Synopsis

The author gives you the knowledge you need to excel at all types of business communication. He shows that all successful business
communication, whether a speech from a podium or a face-to-face conversation, stems from the same basic principles. By using his Five Keys to Successful Communication anyone can unlock the potential to become a great communicator in any medium.
